                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 319.112C64/1.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Price</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>
                        </placeName>, <lb/>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-02-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 16, 1915</hi>
                        </date>,</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your February 14, 7 a.m. and midnight. Insist upon immediate thorough
                    investigation Panaman authorities and fixing responsibility for Cocoa Grove
                    affray. You will, of course, conclude your own investigation, co-operating with
                    other American authorities.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
